com.nifcloud.mbaas.core

Class NCMBPush

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nifcloud.mbaas.core.NCMBBase
      • com.nifcloud.mbaas.core.NCMBPush

  • public class NCMBPush
extends NCMBBase
    NCMBPush is used to retrieve and send the push notification.
    NCMBPush can not add any field.
    Information about the field names that can be set , refer to the following reference .
    See Also:
    NIFCLOUD mobile backend API Reference(Japanese)
